            builder.AddMarkupContent(2, @"<p>
   The Electra QT Wallet is a GUI (Graphical User Interface) version of the headless or daemon wallet. The headless wallet is all command line based. The QT Wallet gives users a way to easily store and transfer Crypto. Currently, the QT is the most widely used wallet at this time. You can learn more about QT by viewing this link <a href=""https://qt.io"">QT</a>.
